headline: BASSÉ AND NESTLÉ MIX IT UP FOR AN ICONIC COLLABORATION
summary: Proudly Canadian and based in Laval, Bassé Nuts, a company known for its premium nut and snack mixes, is thrilled to announce a strategic partnership with Nestlé Canada. This collaboration brings Coffee Crisp and Turtles, two iconic Canadian chocolate brands, into the snack aisle like never before, remixed as flavour-packed, affordable, gourmet nut blends.
